precis:
Enactment of the SASKATCHEWAN MILK ORDER which grants authority to The Milk
Control Board of Saskatchewan to regulate the marketing of cow's milk or
cream produced in Saskatchewan for consumer use in liquid form in both
interprovincial and export trade.
